== Support for Editing Augeas Code ==

[http://augeas.net Augeas] is a tool to surgically edit Unix configuration files. It can be used to change single entries in a configuration file without accidentally overwriting other parts. A prominent application using Augeas is the configuration management system Puppet.

Augeas mode is a major mode to provide support writing Augeas code. It is still at an early stage and currently provides basic keyword fontification.

The latest version is available from https://github.com/smoeding/emacs-augeas-mode

-- StefanMoeding

